<br>
Step 2: Silent Song of Quellious everything in the room with no line-of-sight needed (use Eye or Bind Sight, if necessary to target those hidden ones).<br>
<br>
Step 3: Single pull even the nastiest of rooms with ease and bask in the applause of your peers, as is your due, Maestro.<br>
<br>
Seriously, my bard guildmate used Eye of Zomm clicky and Silent Song of Quellious to single pull Crypt of Decay with complete ease. I'd gladly let her pull for me anytime, anywhere.<br>
