<br>
1.) Snare the mob you want.<br>
<br>
2.) Run it and 6 of it's friends near enough to your group to see it, but still out of agro range.<br>
<br>
3.) Shoot arrows at your slow target as it's 6 friends pound you into oblivion.<br>
<br>
4.) After you die* and the 6 adds wander off have the MT tag the one you snared. <br>
<br>
5.) Have the cleric battle rez you, fight with rez effects.<br>
<br>
6.) Rinse, lather and repeat.<br>
<br>
* - Method not reccomended for standard exp groups. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :o --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/embarassed.gif ALT=":o"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
